  . Experience  the true  hunting  experience on your PC.  Deer Hunter 2005 .
    takes  the  best-selling PC  hunting  franchise to  a new  level.  With
    all-new  graphics and gameplay,  DH  2005 represents to the most robust
    hunting experience available. 

    * The most realistic, accurate and addictive hunting game ever made. 

    * New graphics and gameplay from Southlogic 

    * Multi-player action for up to 12 players via a LAN or the Internet 

    * More sophisticated animal behavior models for increased gameplay
      depth and challenge. 

    * New Custom Map Editor, allowing fans to create their own hunting
      scenarios 

    * 8 hunting sites including locales such as the Pacific Northwest, the
      Southeast, the Northeast, Canada, Australia and Germany 

    * Six species of deer including  the Australian Sambar Deer  and the
      European Roe Deer
